msgstr ""

#: ../../../arch/x86/amd_hsmp.rst:26
msgid ""
"amd_hsmp driver under drivers/platforms/x86/amd/hsmp/ has separate driver "
"files for ACPI object based probing, platform device based probing and for "
"the common code for these two drivers."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../arch/x86/amd_hsmp.rst:30
msgid ""
"Kconfig option CONFIG_AMD_HSMP_PLAT compiles plat.c and creates amd_hsmp.ko. "
"Kconfig option CONFIG_AMD_HSMP_ACPI compiles acpi.c and creates hsmp_acpi."
"ko. Selecting any of these two configs automatically selects "
"CONFIG_AMD_HSMP. This compiles common code hsmp.c and creates hsmp_common.ko "
"module."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../arch/x86/amd_hsmp.rst:35
msgid ""
"Both the ACPI and plat drivers create the miscdevice /dev/hsmp to let user "
"space programs run hsmp mailbox commands."
